{% doc %}
  @prompt
    Create a premium service Hero section for Shopify Pages.
    
    Only focus on:
    
    Layout
    Image
    H1
    Buttons
    Mobile responsiveness  service based  use white black and red theme 
    Connect the Hero section to Shopify Page Dynamic Sources.
    
    Support these Page metafields:
    
    custom.badge_text
    custom.hero_subheading
    custom.hero_image
    custom.hero_image_alt
    custom.hero_image_caption
    custom.hero_image_title
    custom.primary_cta_text
    custom.primary_cta_link
    custom.secondary_cta_text
    custom.secondary_cta_link
    custom.service_area
    custom.phone_number
    custom.google_rating
    custom.google_review_count
    custom.google_review_url
    custom.target_keywords
    
    Only display fields when they contain data.
    
    Use sensible fallbacks., Connect all Page metafields using Shopify Dynamic Sources.
    
    Now it connects:
    
    Hero image
    Badge
    Rating
    CTA
    Service area
    Prompt 3 — Design
    
    Then:
    
    Improve typography, spacing, animations, SVG icons, floating cards and premium styling., Completely refine and enhance the existing Service Hero section.
    
    Do NOT rebuild the section.
    
    Keep all current functionality and dynamic metafields.
    
    This is a premium local service landing page, not an ecommerce page.
    
    The goal is to create a Hero that instantly tells both Google and visitors:
    
    • What service is offered
    • Where it is offered
    • Why this business is trusted
    • How to get a quote
    
    while remaining lightweight, mobile-first and SEO focused.
    
    --------------------------------
    FIX EXISTING ISSUES
    --------------------------------
    
    1. Fix all Shopify Rich Text metafields.
    
    Do not output raw JSON.
    
    Render Rich Text properly using Shopify's rich text rendering.
    
    This applies to:
    
    - Hero Subheading
    - Service Area
    - Any Rich Text metafields
    
    --------------------------------
    VISUAL DESIGN
    --------------------------------
    
    Redesign the Hero to feel like a premium service business.
    
    White background.
    
    Strong red accent.
    
    Modern typography.
    
    Excellent spacing.
    
    Large bold H1.
    
    Professional SVG icons.
    
    Premium shadows.
    
    Rounded corners.
    
    Responsive.
    
    Fast.
    
    No horizontal scrolling.
    
    --------------------------------
    IMAGE CARD
    --------------------------------
    
    The hero image should become the visual focal point.
    
    Large rounded image.
    
    Premium shadow.
    
    Subtle hover animation.
    
    Overlay information cards.
    
    Use dynamic Page metafields.
    
    Overlay cards should include:
    
    ✓ Same Day Available
    
    ✓ Fully Insured
    
    ✓ 5.0 Google Rating
    
    ✓ 112+ Reviews
    
    ✓ Sydney Wide
    
    ✓ Oversized Van
    
    Only display cards when corresponding metafields exist.
    
    Make these cards floating over the image similar to premium SaaS websites.
    
    --------------------------------
    INSTANT UNDERSTANDING
    --------------------------------
    
    Within 3 seconds a visitor should understand:
    
    Furniture Delivery Ryde
    
    Professional Furniture Delivery
    
    Same Day Available
    
    Furniture Protected
    
    Oversized Van
    
    5-Star Rated
    
    Fast Quotes
    
    Sydney Wide
    
    Show these as premium badges around the hero.
    
    --------------------------------
    TRUST BAR
    --------------------------------
    
    Below the Hero create a modern trust bar.
    
    Loop through:
    
    custom.trust_points
    
    Display as animated SVG icon badges.
    
    --------------------------------
    LOCAL SEO
    --------------------------------
    
    Use the Service Area metafield naturally.
    
    Instead of dumping suburbs.
    
    Create natural wording like:
    
    "Proudly servicing Ryde, West Ryde, North Ryde, Putney, Meadowbank and surrounding Sydney suburbs."
    
    --------------------------------
    GOOGLE REVIEW BLOCK
    --------------------------------
    
    Display dynamically:
    
    ★★★★★
    
    Google Rating
    
    Review Count
    
    Button
    
    Read Google Reviews
    
    Use:
    
    custom.google_rating
    
    custom.google_review_count
    
    custom.google_review_url
    
    --------------------------------
    CTA
    --------------------------------
    
    Primary CTA
    
    Get Free Quote
    
    Secondary CTA
    
    Call Now
    
    Buttons should remain dynamic.
    
    --------------------------------
    IMAGE SEO
    --------------------------------
    
    Improve image SEO.
    
    Use:
    
    custom.hero_image
    
    custom.hero_image_alt
    
    custom.hero_image_caption
    
    custom.hero_image_title
    
    Render image inside:
    
    <figure>
    
    <img>
    
    <figcaption>
    
    Lazy load where appropriate.
    
    Responsive.
    
    --------------------------------
    DYNAMIC SCHEMA ENGINE
    --------------------------------
    
    Automatically generate:
    
    WebPage
    
    Service
    
    LocalBusiness
    
    BreadcrumbList
    
    ImageObject
    
    ContactPoint
    
    Use:
    
    Page Title
    
    Page URL
    
    Hero Image
    
    Hero Image Alt
    
    Hero Image Caption
    
    Service Area
    
    Phone Number
    
    Google Rating
    
    Review Count
    
    Schema Service Type
    
    Schema Area Served
    
    Schema Price Range
    
    Only generate schema when data exists.
    
    Do not require manually pasting JSON-LD.
    
    --------------------------------
    MOBILE EXPERIENCE
    --------------------------------
    
    This Hero must be designed primarily for mobile.
    
    Image should appear immediately.
    
    Overlay cards must remain readable.
    
    Buttons full width.
    
    One-hand usability.
    
    No horizontal scrolling.
    
    Above the fold.
    
    --------------------------------
    PERFORMANCE
    --------------------------------
    
    No unnecessary JavaScript.
    
    No heavy animations.
    
    No external libraries.
    
    Optimise for Core Web Vitals.
    
    Optimise for Google Ads landing pages.
    
    --------------------------------
    FINAL GOAL
    --------------------------------
    
    The Hero should feel comparable to the quality of Stripe, Airbnb, Apple and leading Australian service websites.
    
    The page should immediately communicate professionalism, trust and local expertise while remaining highly optimised for SEO, structured data, Google Images and AI-powered search., The Rich Text Page metafields are currently rendering as raw JSON instead of formatted content.
    
    Fix all Rich Text metafields throughout this section.
    
    Do not output the metafield object directly.
    
    Render Rich Text correctly using Shopify Liquid rich text rendering.
    
    This applies to:
    
    - custom.hero_subheading
    - custom.service_area
    - any other Rich Text metafields
    
    The output should display clean paragraphs and formatting, never JSON.
    
    Use conditional checks so empty Rich Text metafields do not render.
    
    Maintain semantic HTML and accessibility., Review and upgrade the existing Service Hero section.
    
    Do not rebuild from scratch unless required. Keep it as a Shopify Page section.
    
    Confirm and support these Page metafields:
    
    custom.badge_text
    custom.hero_subheading
    custom.hero_image
    custom.hero_image_alt
    custom.hero_image_caption
