    Generate AggregateRating only if google_rating and google_review_count exist and are visible on the page.
    
    Use:
    page.title
    page.url
    hero_image
    hero_image_alt
    hero_image_caption
    service_area
    phone_number
    google_rating
    google_review_count
    schema_service_type
    schema_area_served
    schema_price_range
    
    Do not require manual JSON-LD.
    
    Core Web Vitals:
    Use lightweight CSS.
    No heavy JavaScript.
    No external libraries.
    Use responsive image sizes.
    Lazy-load non-critical images.
    Avoid layout shift.
    Keep CSS scoped to this section.
    
    Final goal:
    The section should instantly explain the service, area, trust signals and quote action within 3 seconds, while staying fast, responsive, SEO-friendly and conversion-focused., Now audit the section like a senior Shopify developer, mobile UX designer, CRO expert and technical SEO specialist.
    
    Fix anything that could hurt:
    Mobile layout
    Core Web Vitals
    SEO schema
    Rich Text rendering
    Image SEO
