    Do not remove dynamic metafields.
    Do not add ecommerce elements.
    Make it production-ready., Update the existing Service Hero section.
    
    Add support for this Page metafield:
    
    custom.overlay_highlights
    
    Type: List of single line text.
    
    Use this metafield to create tick/check style overlay cards on the hero image.
    
    Each overlay item should display as:
    
    ✓ Same Day Available
