    Loop through custom.trust_points and display them as trust badges below the hero content.
    
    Keep all existing metafields working.
    
    Do not remove schema, image SEO, CTAs, rating, or service area.
    
    Keep the section fast, mobile-first, and SEO-friendly.   make it compacted overall section full width screen , Update the existing Service Hero section.
    
